response.overview: A world weary and disgruntled 60 year old Captain Logan procures a time machine from a relunctant Brandon Grimm to travel back to 1996 and stop himself from reviewing superhero movies, which will become unwatchable by 2044. But will he create a worse future than he can imagine in the process? And what is Doomsvince's stake in this ill-conceived plan?
response.tagline: A superhero movie about reviewing superhero movies that literally rewinds the history of superhero movies.
response.title: Superhero Rewind - The Movie
